>> title: Last Word
>> tags: gin,coupe,shaken,four-ingredient

Chill a #coupe{} in the freezer.

Fill a #cocktail shaker{} with @ice{}.

Add @lemon juice{1%oz}, @green Chartreuse{1%oz}, @maraschino liqueur{1%oz}, and @gin{1 1/2%oz}.

Shake for at least 30 seconds.

Serve in #coupe{}, garnish with @lemon twist{1}.